idea-plugin.description:
This plugin adds an additional "new-file-menu" entry, to add new release script files with semi-automatically generated names.
A release script file name adheres to this pattern: &lt;timestamp&gt;_[&lt;ticket-type&gt;&lt;ticket-number&gt;_]&lt;description&gt;.&lt;suffix&gt;
The user is guided by a small creation dialog, allowing him to opt out of using a ticket system, or defining ticket type, number and description.
